100% Unofficial Worlds Cup Guide - 2014  UK

100 Pages | True PDF | English | 16 MB 


The 100% unofficial Ultimate World Cup Guide 2014 is your essential at-a-glance guide to everything Brazil 2014. We have analysed every team, every star man, every captain, every manager and every gruelling qualification journey. We have looked at the 12 stadiums in-depth and we have rummaged through history to bring you the World Cup Scrapbook of your dreams.
